<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹快速地吃完早餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他非常饿，但也希望快点见到杰佩托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向农民道谢后，他离开房子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>穿过田野，回到了最开始的那条路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹走了一段时间，他在路上看到了熟悉的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看，这里是傻瓜福地。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时后，他说，“看，那是我遇到狐狸和猫的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想到自己愚蠢的行为，他努力控制住自己的泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又过了几个小时，他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看，那是我从木偶师傅手里逃出来的地方！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噢，多么精彩的冒险啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是回家的路程太长了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我已经走了一天了，还是离家很远。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹坐在树干上哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他累了，他非常想念杰佩托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正当他哭的时候，他听到了一个柔和的声音叫着他的名字：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“匹诺曹……匹诺曹。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这儿！”匹诺曹喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看看四周，想知道声音是从哪里传来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一阵风声传来，还伴着许多掉落的羽毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，原来你在这里！我已经找了你一个多月了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只英俊的老鹰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在找我？你怎么知道我的名字？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，我是杰佩托的老朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121878</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我还在蛋里的时候他救了我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我听说他丢失了孩子，就想帮助他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，我喊着你的名字到处飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>找到你真高兴！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹又蹦又跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你认识杰佩托！噢，太棒了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我马上就能见到我爸爸了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，其实没有你想得那么快。”老鹰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”匹诺曹担心地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当他发现你放学没回家之后，杰佩托找遍了树林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他找遍了这个村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他找遍了整个意大利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在搜寻了一个月之后，他决定坐船去西西里和撒丁岛去找你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他建了一艘船，准备今天就出发。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了！我需要快点儿到达那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鹰先生，你能帮助我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然！我很乐意帮助朋友。”他回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鹰用它的爪子轻轻地抓起匹诺曹，飞向了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他身下，匹诺曹能看见森林，乡村和大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鹰挥舞着翅膀，匹诺曹可以看到沙滩和人群。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把我放到这里。”他用手指着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鹰慢慢地把匹诺曹放在沙滩上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你好运，匹诺曹。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你！”匹诺曹回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹跑向人群，寻找着杰佩托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，请问杰佩托在哪里？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁是杰佩托？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰佩托是我爸爸。他有灰色的头发和慈祥的笑容。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个看热闹的人看起来很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看见那边那艘小船了吗？那就是杰佩托。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹朝海上的波浪看去，看到了一个棕色的小点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢！他走得太远了。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看这天！马上就要下雨了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸可能会掉进水里。我必须帮助他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在被阻止之前，匹诺曹已经跳进了大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始游向杰佩托的船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>